I. Position Summary
The position is responsible for performing testing and determining the best way to be carried out. The incumbent acts as coordinator to facilitate communication with related parties of test programs and provides technical support to Project Manager in EMC department.
该职位负责执行测试并确定最佳执行方式。作为协调者，促进测试项目相关方的沟通，并为EMC部门的项目经理提供技术支持。

II. Job Responsibilities
1. Define test plan & execute test program; (20%)
制定测试计划并执行测试项目；
2. Generate and issue test reports; (20%)
生成并发布测试报告；
3. Provide essential support to team to ensure the quality of the tests and recommendation for enhancing test 
features; (20%)
为团队提供必要的支持，以确保测试的质量，并为增强测试功能提供建议;
4. Maintain daily project operations and provide technical support to ongoing projects; (30%)
维护日常项目运作，为正在进行的项目提供技术支持;
5. Manage and control projects and reports to Project Manager on status of the project; (5%)
管理和控制项目，并向项目经理汇报项目状态;
6. Coordinate all product development activities with suppliers and internal departments, especially with the customer 
service department. (5%)
协调所有与供应商和内部部门的产品开发活动，特别是与客户服务部门。

III. Job Requirements 
1. Bachelor Degree holder in Electric, Electronic Engineering or related discipline;
大专或本科学历，电气、电子工程或相关专业;
2. Experience in industrial products testing is an advantage but not mandatory;
有测试行业工作经验者优先考虑，但非强制要求;
3 Good understanding on EMC and radio testing for household and lighting products;
熟悉 EMC 测试或相关的无线电/电气设备;
4 Fluent in spoken and written in English and Chinese;
流利的中英文口语和书写能力;
5 Task-oriented and team player.
任务导向和团队合作精神。
